title: Simeon outlasts Morgan Park 68-64 for city championship
text:
Simeon outlasts Morgan Park 68-64 for city championship Simeon vs. Morgan Park Nuccio DiNuzzo / Chicago Tribune 
Simeon's Marquis Brown reacts after making a basket against Morgan Park during the first half of their city championship game at the Jones Convocation Center at Chicago State University on Sunday, Feb. 19, 2017.
